9	Maintainability	6	Good comments, but 1 000-line blob is pain to diff; no tests.
10	Deployment Readiness	6.5	Works over http://localhost; no .env, no CI, sessions drop on refresh.
11	MacBook-M2 Fit	9	Zero Docker, nothing heavy; instant launch on 8 GB.
Composite vibe: 7.1 / 10 ‚Üí ‚Äúworks, but still beta.‚Äù

How to slam every column to 11/10 (TL;DR)
Split the beast ‚Üí secureStorage.js, apiController.js, agentContext.js, ui.js, collaborationHub.js; load with <script type="module">.

Secrets harden ‚Üí move the AES key to indexedDB, add Content-Security-Policy + COEP headers, drop localStorage.

Persistence ‚Üí POST/GET /api/sessions to file or SQLite; restore on load.

DX rocket fuel ‚Üí npm scripts: dev (live-server 8080), lint, test; add ESLint + Prettier.

Token shredder ‚Üí stream completions, pipe fragments to UI; summarise old history with GPT-4 mini to 3-line gists.

Hot-reload backend ‚Üí nodemon proxy-server.js; .env for port & key fallback.

UI polish ‚Üí Tailwind + dark-mode toggle; drag-drop files to feed agents.

Perf tweaks ‚Üí Serve static with HTTP/2 + gzip; preload fonts; throttle resize observers.

Tests ‚Üí Vitest unit tests for utils; Playwright E2E happy-path.

CI / CD ‚Üí GitHub Actions matrix: lint ‚Üí test ‚Üí build; auto-bump changelog.

Cluster-ready ‚Üí Wrap proxy in PM2; graceful shutdown; Redis queue for OpenAI calls.

Ship those, every row flips green. üü©

